What I have learned/executed/created so far:

CUT THE COUNTRY
LAYER→ TRANSPARENCY→ ALPHA CHANNEL→ RIGHT CLICK TO CLEAR→ ADD FOOD
TURN OFF EYE ON MAP TO RESIZE FOOD IN THE SHAPE OF THE COUNTRY

TOOLS, SELECT FOR CUTTING

TO CROP→ DRAW BOX AROUND PICTURE TO EDIT

TO RESIZE→ RIGHT CLICK, SCALE, SCALE IMAGE


Select food layer you want to create
Move layer to top, above map
Right click, Layer → Scale Layer
Select crop tool and make sure Current Layer only is checked (in toolbox)
Draw square around desired portion of image and press Enter
Move picture to desired location using 4-arrow moving tool
To see what overall picture looks like, move map to top layer
